extends ManagedObjectDefinition<ExternalHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfgClient,ExternalHTTPAccessLogPublisherCfg>
    An interface for querying the External HTTP Access Log Publisher managed object definition meta information.

    External HTTP Access Log Publishers publish HTTP access messages to an external handler.
